10 An act relating to establishing a pilot for community nurse programs
11 serving aging Vermonters
12 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
13 Sec. 1. COMMUNITY NURSE PROGRAM PILOT SERVING AGING
14 VERMONTERS
15 (a) $450,000.00 shall be appropriated to the Department of Disabilities,
16 Aging, and Independent Living for the purpose of establishing a two-year pilot
17 to enhance the provision of services by one or more existing community nurse
18 programs to aging Vermonters in the program’s region.
19 (b) The Department shall seek and consider applications for participation in
20 the pilot described in this section from existing community nurse programs
